    "description": "<strong>《至暗之光》</strong>是一款拥有特殊玩法的科幻类平台动作游戏。在一个充满超自然生物的赛博朋克末日世界里冒险吧！利用你自身和无人机伙伴的能力生存下去，增强自己，击败那些潜伏于黑暗的怪物。只有你的<strong>无人机</strong>光源才能探测到它们。 体验恐惧，感受他们的存在，因为他们围绕着你。  <br><br><br><br>你是一个暗黑狩猎者，身处于一个支离破碎的世界。为了生存，你需要武装自己，披荆斩棘杀出一条路，并收集被杀死的黑暗生物身上的‘碎片‘来让自己变得更强。在求生路上，你会充分体会到这个黑暗末日世界的神秘。<br><br><br><br><strong>游戏特色</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>电影级画质，细致的人物和环境设计，生动的动画效果能给你带来一场丰富的视觉盛宴。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/0e5c1a5ec7554c912fa5f504b9f45cda.poster.avif?t=1731487580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/0e5c1a5ec7554c912fa5f504b9f45cda.webm?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/0e5c1a5ec7554c912fa5f504b9f45cda.mp4?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>具有挑战性的战斗，类魂般的战斗系统。 你必须定时攻击，并使用闪避和招架敌人以造成最大伤害。</li></ul>  <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/bcb2bf3b8d5bf330d4e04003c0d82751.poster.avif?t=1731487580\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/bcb2bf3b8d5bf330d4e04003c0d82751.webm?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/bcb2bf3b8d5bf330d4e04003c0d82751.mp4?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/74c0d5d7bd683011a4d0981748e79e34.poster.avif?t=1731487580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/74c0d5d7bd683011a4d0981748e79e34.webm?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/74c0d5d7bd683011a4d0981748e79e34.mp4?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>各类远程，近战和可投掷物品以及特殊的道具。还有多种方法能升级武器和装备，让你的角色技能更加丰富。</li></ul>  <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/7ad31b0ae57956123c57c8e19708355b.poster.avif?t=1731487580\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/7ad31b0ae57956123c57c8e19708355b.webm?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/7ad31b0ae57956123c57c8e19708355b.mp4?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>非线性的地图结构能让你选择自己的方式去探索那些黑暗区域，遇到可怕的超自然敌人以及恐怖的boss。不过当然，你也会在游戏里遇到一些友好的NPC给你提供帮助。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/1b4e2793549e042bfd05b9d69e62b014.poster.avif?t=1731487580\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/1b4e2793549e042bfd05b9d69e62b014.webm?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/1b4e2793549e042bfd05b9d69e62b014.mp4?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>利用你身边的小无人机射出的光来调查那些隐形的敌人并找到隐藏道路。</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在经典像素模式下玩游戏!</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/1e1401bbde6532950fe0e8d1347c871f.poster.avif?t=1731487580\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/1e1401bbde6532950fe0e8d1347c871f.webm?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1134520/extras/1e1401bbde6532950fe0e8d1347c871f.mp4?t=1731487580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
